%^BOLD%^-=%^BLACK%^Cavern Domain%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

The cavern domain focuses upon the secret dark places 
within the earth.  As such, it draws upon stone and 
darkness, and its spells are strengthened by being 
in such surroundings in some cases.

The cavern domain contains the following spells:
Meld into Stone (2nd), Maw of Stone (5th), and Earthquake (8th)

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: The Faceless One

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
     